      "id": "urn:samm:io.catenax.quality_task:3.0.0#QualityTask",
      "label": "QualityTask",
      "kind": "Aspect",
      "preferredName": "QualityTasks",
      "description": "For Catena-X business case Quality Management. Supported technical features: delta update feature, meta information feature and can be used along the supply chain - also for supplier-to-supplier data exchange. The supported model features are described in detail in the Catena-X Quality KIT. This model is used to exchange quality tasks. A quality task is used to link  information from different Catena-X Quality Management data models together."
    },
